Dialogue: 0,1:31:36.20,1:31:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And surrendering perception to God and asking to have the truth revealed to you,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.99,1:31:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,removes the linear.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.59,1:31:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you see the nonlinear.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.09,1:31:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.94,1:31:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So that the innocence,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.52,1:31:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the basic innocence,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.84,1:31:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,which the Course talks about,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.16,1:31:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes apparent.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.68,1:31:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I like Socrates' statement,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.88,1:32:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,because it makes it more apparent that everyone is innocent
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.84,1:32:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,because they firmly believe that which they are pursuing.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.80,1:32:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.60,1:32:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.13,1:32:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And so responsibility is limited
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.64,1:32:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,because the nature of the human mind is such that intrinsically,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.46,1:32:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,it's unable to discern truth from falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.34,1:32:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.84,1:32:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not built for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.96,1:32:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not capable of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.96,1:32:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And is there a physical desire to move this energy through the body in order to affect that?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.68,1:32:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe in moving energies through the body.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.72,1:32:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.44,1:32:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.27,1:32:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.85,1:32:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want a picture breathing up the energy to a higher chakra,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.69,1:32:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,that's probably harmless.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.66,1:33:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's the intention behind it, not the breathing itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.25,1:33:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.69,1:33:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.81,1:33:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Our study group has chosen the topic of, here, the energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.69,1:33:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Humility to discuss.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.41,1:33:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was wondering if you could say something to us about radical humility.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.07,1:33:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I know more about humility than anybody walking under your planet.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.53,1:33:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,After you've hit bottom, you know what humility means, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.74,1:33:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, humility really ensues from the reality of the understanding of the limitations of the human mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.75,1:33:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't so much a spiritual prostration, you know, you're not spiritually prostrating yourself with ashes and sackcloth.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.93,1:34:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more just honesty.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.73,1:34:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So humility comes out of intrinsic honesty.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.32,1:34:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In and of itself, you can't tell who's telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.00,1:34:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, let's take something currently in the media.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.80,1:34:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no way of knowing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.52,1:34:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what's the truth?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.32,1:34:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.66,1:34:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you're not a calibrator.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.94,1:34:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you know right away who's telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.58,1:34:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But the mind, in and of itself, is not able to comprehend that.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.34,1:34:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So out of accepting the reality comes the humility.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.84,1:34:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.53,1:34:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That, to me, would be the highest form of acceptance.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.97,1:34:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Would be through understanding the nature of the human mind, you automatically become humble.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.20,1:34:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you cannot tell truth from falsehood on its own.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:50.77,1:34:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes a jury of 12 people.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:52.73,1:34:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And they spend months.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.97,1:35:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And at the end of that time, they don't know whether they're right or not.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.51,1:35:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, DNA testing.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.87,1:35:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, DNA testing, they took off 165 people off death row across the United States.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.75,1:35:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,165 people falsely condemned to death.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.67,1:35:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was the wrong person.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.24,1:35:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And scientific research shows that visual identification in crime scenes is 50% an error.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.72,1:35:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,They line people up.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.13,1:35:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the one that did it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.13,1:35:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The chances are 50-50 that person is correct.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.13,1:35:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,50-50.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.13,1:35:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd hate to have my life hanging on 50-50, wouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.13,1:35:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,With somebody that's nearsighted and was half-bombed at the time they looked at you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.36,1:35:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the one.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.36,1:35:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My God.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.36,1:35:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.36,1:35:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So even under the best of circumstances, swearing an oath, the error is 50%.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:38.36,1:35:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though somebody's life is hanging on.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.36,1:35:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I'm not saying that's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.36,1:35:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not saying that's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.36,1:35:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not saying that's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.36,1:35:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm saying that's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.36,1:35:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not saying that's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.36,1:35:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not saying that's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.36,1:35:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not saying that's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.36,1:35:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not saying that's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.36,1:35:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not saying that's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.36,1:35:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not saying that's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.90,1:35:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not saying that's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.94,1:35:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not saying that's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:54.94,1:35:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not saying that's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.94,1:35:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.94,1:35:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Never.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:59.06,1:36:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So even under the best of circumstances, swearing an oath, the error is 50%.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.36,1:36:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though somebody's life is hanging on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.46,1:36:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So that shows you how limited.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.30,1:36:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So once you see the limitation of the human mind, then humility is just an automatic consequence
Dialogue: 0,1:36:12.30,1:36:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,of seeing what its limitation is.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.40,1:36:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't use a lawn mower to level a field.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.71,1:36:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's just not capable of doing the job.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.77,1:36:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like when in your day, though, the ego is automatically in the knowing as you're coming across someone,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.00,1:36:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and humility is not something that enters your mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.82,1:36:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, humility is like what I'm telling you about, contemplation.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.44,1:36:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's part of one's attitude, that all information and everything you think are all presumptions.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:51.97,1:36:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all tentative.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.69,1:37:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So you hold thinkingness as tentative, but not as authoritative.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.56,1:37:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's tentative. All evidence is tentative.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.21,1:37:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Perception is just tentative evidence.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.98,1:37:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.62,1:37:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going above 600 and you're leaving the body,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:24.16,1:37:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,would there be any possibility that you have to come back again and reincarnate?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.16,1:37:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you have to come back again after hitting?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:32.18,1:37:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're on the level of 600, would you have to come back for any reason?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:36.18,1:37:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Not for the reasons one would presume, not because it's a have-to due to negative karma,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.46,1:37:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,not because you identify with the linear, but instead you see the options of the non-linear.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.92,1:37:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a choice, I think, made between yourself and divinity.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.98,1:38:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Because friends of mine who are doing some kinesiologic testing got the Dramana Maharshi,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.66,1:38:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,was reincarnated and attended one of your lectures.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:08.60,1:38:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember meeting him.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:11.82,1:38:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's not true?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.26,1:38:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.24,1:38:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He said the world you see is illusion, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.66,1:38:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,although there's no point trying to save the world,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.40,1:38:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,because the world you see doesn't even exist, you know, it's all in your head.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.37,1:38:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That takes humility to accept that.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.57,1:38:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's only a belief system until it becomes true within one's own spiritual evolution.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.43,1:38:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you see that all you're seeing is perception going,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.79,1:38:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,all you're seeing is a run of perception, like TV images.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:53.33,1:39:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he never left that mountain.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.56,1:39:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And I like Susan's sign too.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.80,1:39:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, my question is that today one of the students asked me if I would come up here and ask the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:26.86,1:39:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And throughout the whole day I had severe anxiety.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.00,1:39:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to know, what is this anxiety?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.04,1:39:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this anxiety?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.12,1:39:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, this is the most loving group on earth, and I'm in the presence of divinity in this group,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.40,1:39:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and yet I have this humongous anxiety to come up and ask a question and sit here and let people look at me.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:48.87,1:39:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:52.43,1:39:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to presume that you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.02,1:39:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to presume that you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.88,1:40:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to presume that everybody's thoughts about you are benign.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.82,1:40:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to presume that everybody's thoughts about you are benign.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.16,1:40:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to presume that everybody's happy that you're here.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:07.27,1:40:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.82,1:40:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you presume turns out to be a reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.60,1:40:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody's pleased that you're here and that you're speaking as you're speaking.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.82,1:40:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pleased.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:17.52,1:40:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you pleased?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.41,1:40:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's stage anxiety.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.40,1:40:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's stage fright.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.22,1:40:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's stage fright.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.22,1:40:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.66,1:40:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's stage fright.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.86,1:40:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I had stage fright when I was in kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.03,1:40:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was in kindergarten, they had a class play.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.84,1:40:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was supposed to be a rabbit.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.86,1:40:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was supposed to hide behind this tree.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.86,1:40:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was a big cardboard tree.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.66,1:40:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And on a cue, I was supposed to hop, hop, hop, hop, hop, hop, and then hop behind the tree.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.30,1:40:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.78,1:40:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wouldn't come out.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.08,1:40:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:55.02,1:40:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.32,1:40:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.90,1:41:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And the cue lady kept saying, I didn't need to come out.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.92,1:41:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.52,1:41:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.72,1:41:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.54,1:41:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart was beating fast, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.22,1:41:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.78,1:41:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:06.20,1:41:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Being looked at.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.32,1:41:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Being looked at.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.42,1:41:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's what it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.72,1:41:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Other people looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.92,1:41:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.34,1:41:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I want everybody to shut your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.86,1:41:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.38,1:41:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody agree?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.40,1:41:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.00,1:41:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Just for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.80,1:41:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.70,1:41:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody's looking at you.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.06,1:41:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.72,1:41:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that better?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.98,1:41:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess not.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.92,1:41:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I think I'm looking at myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.64,1:41:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'm judging myself every minute that possibly, you know, I'm not, well, I guess
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.76,1:41:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I put a value judgment on myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:34.80,1:41:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, imitate a person who has, what are we calling this issue, Scott?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.25,1:41:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What have we been calling it before?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.71,1:41:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Stage fright.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.69,1:41:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Stage fright.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.39,1:41:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.17,1:41:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.93,1:41:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Imitate a person who has stage fright.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:48.41,1:41:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Imitate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:54.16,1:41:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're not scared enough, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.80,1:42:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.49,1:42:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.69,1:42:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:06.07,1:42:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't stay calm, I'm going to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.25,1:42:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.89,1:42:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All of a sudden, the anxiety kind of released.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:14.58,1:42:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I stood in line, it released a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.44,1:42:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And now.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.50,1:42:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It seemed like it released more.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.72,1:42:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:21.04,1:42:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I don't know how, why, how, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:23.82,1:42:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You accepted the worst possible scenario, and you saw it was illusion.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:27.58,1:42:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that what happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:28.58,1:42:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.24,1:42:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:31.24,1:42:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.30,1:42:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The way to undo a fear or a phobia, or anything like that, keep going, and then what?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.58,1:42:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And then what?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:39.16,1:42:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They're going to look at me, yeah, and then what?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:40.60,1:42:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they're going to laugh at me, and then what?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:42.12,1:42:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And then they're going to think I'm stupid, and then what?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:44.00,1:42:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And then what?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:44.52,1:42:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And then what?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.80,1:42:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And then what?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.08,1:42:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I'll make a fool out of myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:48.56,1:42:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you keep accepting it.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:51.06,1:42:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, so I'm making a fool out of myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.92,1:42:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Who gives a, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:55.20,1:42:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.24,1:42:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you accept the bottom line, it all goes away.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:59.58,1:43:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why eventually accepting the inevitability of death usually knocks about 95% of the other fears out of the box.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.62,1:43:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Because all of them are symbolic of physical death.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:11.50,1:43:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be poor, then what?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.72,1:43:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I won't have any money.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.58,1:43:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll get kicked out.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:14.82,1:43:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I won't have any place to live.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:16.28,1:43:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll starve to death.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:17.70,1:43:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And then what?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:19.34,1:43:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's always, and then I'll die.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:22.04,1:43:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So once you get down to the bedrock underneath all fears, it's the fear that I'll die.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:27.98,1:43:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to have everybody's approval here, therefore I'll die, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:32.58,1:43:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you, you know, the worst thing that's happened to you is you topple over right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:39.26,1:43:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not so lucky, you're still breathing.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:40.80,1:43:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:41.18,1:43:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:42.36,1:43:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:43.02,1:43:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.30,1:43:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, this really helped me.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.48,1:43:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.84,1:43:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A great deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:47.54,1:43:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're carried.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.16,1:43:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, and thank you, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:49.62,1:43:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye, Sarah.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.04,1:43:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:51.92,1:43:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This is lost music.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:53.38,1:43:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And I took it, and I wanted you to sign it.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:56.88,1:43:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, we'll send it back.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:57.88,1:43:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.38,1:43:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.60,1:44:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I think facing stage fright is very hard.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:01.72,1:44:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It took a lot of courage.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:02.84,1:44:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:03.60,1:44:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:12.10,1:44:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so scared I forgot what she asked.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.00,1:44:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to pray about what she was going to ask me.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:19.25,1:44:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:19.97,1:44:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:20.63,1:44:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That experience you spoke about this morning when you had the temptation that power,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:25.91,1:44:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that power is yours, own it.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:28.59,1:44:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That what?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.89,1:44:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.69,1:44:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The experience when you attempted that power is yours, all power is yours, own it.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:35.73,1:44:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Own it.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:36.79,1:44:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.75,1:44:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What calibration level does that occur at?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:41.04,1:44:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's probably over 850, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:45.00,1:44:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I have permission to ask about the silent communication.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.52,1:44:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It was over 800, 840, 850, 860.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:54.90,1:44:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it comes in around 850 there.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.10,1:45:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if the consciousness is still open,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:00.85,1:45:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,to the Luciferic, at that calibration,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:04.65,1:45:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,then wouldn't it be wise if one's intent was to go above that level?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:11.37,1:45:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:12.57,1:45:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The person's aim is for enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.38,1:45:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But enlightenment isn't that easily acquired.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:17.70,1:45:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And everywhere along the way there's a challenge.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:20.08,1:45:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the challenge there.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:21.96,1:45:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why Christ sweat blood in the Garden of Eden.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:25.74,1:45:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Christ sweat blood.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:28.30,1:45:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The Buddha felt like his bones were broken, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:31.80,1:45:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that which is the antithesis of truth sees you as a great danger.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:38.10,1:45:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you're an ordinary sinner and you go to church and all that crap, you're no nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:42.90,1:45:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And once you start really getting up there, you see what happens is your power is so enormous,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:47.80,1:45:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,you become now a major threat.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:50.69,1:45:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The demons start looking for your weakness.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.94,1:45:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And the fallen gurus, we once did a lecture on them,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:59.65,1:46:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the temptation now comes in and finds the weakness in your armor.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:03.38,1:46:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sexual seduction, flattery, money, having lots of followers, lots of wealth, pomp, circumstance.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:12.38,1:46:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The glamour of that.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.83,1:46:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sooner or later, they're going to find your weakness.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:18.43,1:46:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The pretty girl says, I love you, let's make love, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:23.08,1:46:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is holy, let's be holy.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:25.78,1:46:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have holy sex, you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:27.58,1:46:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They fall into it right and left.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:30.37,1:46:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So, they look.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:31.07,1:46:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's due to lack of preparation at the lower level.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:35.97,1:46:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's lack of a teacher warning you.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.87,1:46:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel the teacher must teach you what the temptations are along the way
Dialogue: 0,1:46:43.87,1:46:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,so that when you get there, you're not blindsided.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:47.65,1:46:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, my antipathy to the United States of America is its stupidity
Dialogue: 0,1:46:51.55,1:46:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,in allowing itself to get blindsided about every 15 minutes about everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:56.68,1:46:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:57.78,1:47:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They sound asleep up there or where are they, you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.23,1:47:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be so sound asleep that you don't know that there's a half a million
Dialogue: 0,1:47:07.16,1:47:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,communists across the border in North Korea?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:10.34,1:47:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't know there's a half a million?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:13.54,1:47:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean plain breathing.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:17.38,1:47:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it possible that someone at a calibration level down here has an intent for up here
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.21,1:47:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,or is it just an illusion?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:26.21,1:47:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No, people tend to evolve.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:28.11,1:47:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They want to evolve consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:29.51,1:47:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They want to evolve.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:31.39,1:47:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's why there's so many people involved in the spiritual work.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.19,1:47:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, religious and spiritual books outsell all others right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:38.69,1:47:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably in the
Dialogue: 0,1:47:39.59,1:47:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,WGW, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:41.09,1:47:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Closures Weekly.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:42.59,1:47:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:43.82,1:47:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's an enormous interest in it.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:47.88,1:47:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:50.29,1:47:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are called, those are called the tests along the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:53.59,1:47:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:55.10,1:47:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I'm going to transcend seduction.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:57.20,1:48:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's like karma says, let's see.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:03.33,1:48:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Good looking.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.63,1:48:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:09.43,1:48:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're not, you're not really clear at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:11.83,1:48:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,After 850, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:12.83,1:48:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always susceptible up to that point.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:14.43,1:48:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're susceptible the whole way.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:19.37,1:48:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,At 850, you could fall for the power.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:21.47,1:48:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it grew as it did because very few through, very few go through that pass at 850.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:27.27,1:48:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so rare that you can see who was there and you see the decision they made.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:31.27,1:48:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And beyond 850?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:33.53,1:48:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in a different realm.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:34.93,1:48:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That temptation doesn't come up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:38.98,1:48:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:41.32,1:48:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond 850 has to do with belief systems about the nature of divinity.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.92,1:48:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The nature of divinity itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:55.91,1:48:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:58.81,1:48:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:00.31,1:49:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I was reading in your truth versus falsehood about that whole idea of alien abduction being false.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.51,1:49:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:09.41,1:49:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have a friend that is absolutely convinced that that's happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:13.91,1:49:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know if this was some kind of, you know, is that some kind of attack?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.41,1:49:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll explain alien abduction to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:20.91,1:49:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to do with, you know, in the New Testament.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.31,1:49:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the name of that chapter that covers the 70 revelations?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:30.89,1:49:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, there are astral realms.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:34.92,1:49:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you can go out of body.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:37.22,1:49:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Your spirit can go out of body and visit an astral realm and experience the reality there and come back.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:42.72,1:49:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And it did experience it only within a psychic level.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:49.90,1:49:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see if I can explain it.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:52.46,1:49:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,People go out of body, the spirit.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:56.55,1:50:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Visits an astral domain and has experiences and comes back.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:02.08,1:50:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There are some that are visited very often in the same report is reported over the centuries.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:11.25,1:50:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The apocalypse, you know, the forecast of John.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:16.02,1:50:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,John calibrated at 70 and the book of Revelations calibrates at about 70.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:21.75,1:50:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a lower astral realm.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:24.15,1:50:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:25.15,1:50:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:26.55,1:50:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to maybe karmic propensity.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:28.45,1:50:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes alcoholism, very commonly temporal lobe epilepsy, various other conditions.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:36.25,1:50:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A person may experience the lower astral realm.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:42.51,1:50:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, it's not like a movie.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:45.30,1:50:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's experiential, very convincing.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:47.70,1:50:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And I knew a teacher here and in Sedona at one time was in a high state and then went into that state and got a whole group to come out here for survival.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:57.56,1:50:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They're going to dig underground.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:58.66,1:50:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They're going to find homes and a lot of crap.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:00.68,1:51:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And he experienced it with such conviction that when he related to others, the conviction is what convinced them.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:07.78,1:51:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Likewise, the similar thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:09.38,1:51:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The conviction is because it was experiential.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:13.14,1:51:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You do experience it.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:16.50,1:51:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:17.50,1:51:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So he experienced a different reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:19.70,1:51:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, it's interesting because it's like there's only a couple movies that are popular or really accessible in the lower astral realm.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:27.00,1:51:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And they tend to replay over and over.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:29.10,1:51:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The end times is over.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:30.70,1:51:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And over again, California falls off in the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:33.90,1:51:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Earthquakes in the middle of New York City, ravaging hordes.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:37.60,1:51:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And anyway, the same apocalyptic forecast recur over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:47.03,1:51:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The one that John experienced this reported in the New Testament has been commonly experienced by people throughout the ages.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:54.43,1:51:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The end times, the end times are forecast, you know, every other week.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:58.98,1:52:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody's got another forecast to the end times.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:01.48,1:52:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a guy.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:01.98,1:52:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And Sedona used to give lectures on the end times.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:04.88,1:52:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And he had a mustache that went up like this, like Salvatore Dali.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:09.28,1:52:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, at the time for the end times came and went, all he did is change the dates.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:16.74,1:52:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any, I think, direction I can send this girl in to make her, you know, I'm concerned about her.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:24.59,1:52:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you concerned about her?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:28.94,1:52:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you like her.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.14,1:52:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She's convinced what?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:31.24,1:52:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The end times are coming?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:34.33,1:52:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, she's just convinced that this is going on.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:36.63,1:52:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:37.23,1:52:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that she needs to find some direction to work her way out of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:42.73,1:52:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I think she's going to recover?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:44.43,1:52:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlikely.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:52.02,1:52:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:52.82,1:52:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It would take karmic research to see why she was prone to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:56.02,1:53:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes after brain injuries, after head injuries, under conditions of extremity, conditions of intoxication, post convulsive fugue, F-U-G-E episodes.
